  <entry>
    <title>MD-一些语法备忘录</title>
    <url>/posts/20260426235727-23499.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>一些常用Markdown语法。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h1 id="标题语法"><a href="#标题语法" class="headerlink" title="标题语法"></a>标题语法</h1><p>在每行前面添加 <strong>#</strong> 号用来实现标题，一级标题一个#号，二级标题两个#号，以此类推值第六标题。</p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="section"># header</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>[!NOTE] <strong>可选语法</strong><br>还可以在标题下方添加 &#x3D;&#x3D;&#x3D; 或 — 用来作为分隔符</p>
</blockquote>
<br>

<h1 id="段落"><a href="#段落" class="headerlink" title="段落"></a>段落</h1><p>可以使用单行空白分割段落。</p>
<br>

<h1 id="换行"><a href="#换行" class="headerlink" title="换行"></a>换行</h1><p><del>在一行的末尾添加两个或多个空格，然后按回车键,即可创建一个换行。</del><b>直接使用<code>&lt;br&gt;</code>来实现。</b></p>
<figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是一段话    </span><br><span class="line">这就完成了换行</span><br><span class="line">或者通过输入<span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line">来实现换行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<br>

<h1 id="空格占位符"><a href="#空格占位符" class="headerlink" title="空格占位符"></a>空格占位符</h1><p>直接写入HTML语法</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="symbol">&amp;ensp;</span> 写入半方大空白</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">&amp;emsp;</span> 写入一个中文字符的全方大空白</span><br><span class="line"><span class="symbol">&amp;nbsp;</span> 一个普通的空白</span><br><span class="line">$~~~$ 用来写入连续的空格字符，四个个~相当于一个中文字符大小</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<br>

<h1 id="强调"><a href="#强调" class="headerlink" title="强调"></a>强调</h1><ul>
<li><h2 id="粗体"><a href="#粗体" class="headerlink" title="粗体"></a>粗体</h2></li>
</ul>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Markdown语法</th>
<th>预览效果</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td><code>I just love **bold text**.</code></td>
<td>I just love <strong>bold text</strong>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>I just love __bold text__.</code></td>
<td>I just love <strong>bold text</strong>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>Love**is**bold</code></td>
<td>Love<strong>is</strong>bold</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<ul>
<li><h2 id="斜体"><a href="#斜体" class="headerlink" title="斜体"></a>斜体</h2></li>
</ul>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Markdown语法</th>
<th>预览效果</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td><code>Italicized text is the *cat&#39;s meow*.</code></td>
<td>Italicized text is the <em>cat’s meow</em>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>Italicized text is the _cat&#39;s meow_.</code></td>
<td>Italicized text is the <em>cat’s meow</em>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>A*cat*meow</code></td>
<td>A<em>cat</em>meow</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<ul>
<li><h2 id="强调和斜体"><a href="#强调和斜体" class="headerlink" title="强调和斜体"></a>强调和斜体</h2></li>
</ul>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Markdown语法</th>
<th>预览效果</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td><code>This text is ***really important***.</code></td>
<td>This text is <strong><em>really important</em></strong>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>This text is ___really important___.</code></td>
<td>This text is <strong><em>really important</em></strong>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>This text is __*really important*__.</code></td>
<td>This text is <strong><em>really important</em></strong>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>This text is **_really important_**.</code></td>
<td>This text is <strong><em>really important</em></strong>.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>This is really***very***important text.</code></td>
<td>This is really**<em>very</em>**important text.</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<br>

<h1 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h1><p>使用’&gt;’来进行引用<br>引用文献则采用<code>^[]</code>形式</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[^1]</span><br><span class="line">[^1]:URL</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<br>

<h1 id="列表"><a href="#列表" class="headerlink" title="列表"></a>列表</h1><ul>
<li><h2 id="有序列表"><a href="#有序列表" class="headerlink" title="有序列表"></a>有序列表</h2></li>
</ul>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Markdown语法</th>
<th>预览效果</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td><code>1. First item   2. Second item   3. Third item   4. Fourth item</code></td>
<td>1. First item<br>2. Second item<br>3. Third item<br>4. Fourth item</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>1. First item   1. Second item   1. Third item   1. Fourth item</code></td>
<td>1. First item<br>2. Second item<br>3. Third item<br>4. Fourth item</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>1. First item   8. Second item   3. Third item   5. Fourth item</code></td>
<td>1. First item<br>2. Second item<br>3. Third item<br>4. Fourth item</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>1. First item   2. Second item   3. Third item       1. Indented item       2. Indented item   4. Fourth item</code></td>
<td>1. First item<br>2. Second item<br>3. Third item<br>    1. Indented item<br>    2. Indented item<br>4. Fourth item</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<ul>
<li><h2 id="无序列表"><a href="#无序列表" class="headerlink" title="无序列表"></a>无序列表</h2></li>
</ul>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th></th>
<th></th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td><code>-First item   - Second item   - Third item   - Fourth item</code></td>
<td>- First item<br>- Second item<br>- Third item<br>- Fourth item</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>* First item   * Second item   * Third item   * Fourth item</code></td>
<td>- First item<br>- Second item<br>- Third item<br>- Fourth item</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>+ First item   + Second item   + Third item   + Fourth item</code></td>
<td>- First item<br>- Second item<br>- Third item<br>- Fourth item</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><code>- First item   - Second item   - Third item       - Indented item       - Indented item   - Fourth item</code></td>
<td>- First item<br>- Second item<br>- Third item<br>    - Indented item<br>    - Indented item<br>- Fourth item</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td></td>
<td></td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<br>

<h1 id="分隔符"><a href="#分隔符" class="headerlink" title="分隔符"></a>分隔符</h1><p>直接使用 <code>ctrl+alt+f</code> 的快捷键即可</p>
<br>

<h1 id="超链接"><a href="#超链接" class="headerlink" title="超链接"></a>超链接</h1><p>超链接Markdown语法代码：<code>[超链接显示名](超链接地址 &quot;超链接title&quot;)</code></p>
<p>对应的HTML代码：<code>&lt;a href=&quot;超链接地址&quot; title=&quot;超链接title&quot;&gt;超链接显示名&lt;/a&gt;</code></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是一个链接 [Markdown语法](https://markdown.com.cn)。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>渲染效果如下：</p>
<p>这是一个链接 <a href="https://markdown.com.cn/">Markdown语法</a>。</p>
<h2 id="给链接增加-Title"><a href="#给链接增加-Title" class="headerlink" title="给链接增加 Title"></a>给链接增加 Title</h2><p>链接title是当鼠标悬停在链接上时会出现的文字，这个title是可选的，它放在圆括号中链接地址后面，跟链接地址之间以空格分隔。</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">这是一个链接 [Markdown语法](https://markdown.com.cn &quot;最好的markdown教程&quot;)。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>渲染效果如下：</p>
<p>这是一个链接 <a href="https://markdown.com.cn/" title="最好的markdown教程">Markdown语法</a>。</p>
<br>

<h2 id="网址和Email地址"><a href="#网址和Email地址" class="headerlink" title="网址和Email地址"></a>网址和Email地址</h2><p>使用尖括号可以很方便地把URL或者email地址变成可点击的链接。</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;https://markdown.com.cn&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;fake@example.com&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>渲染效果如下：</p>
<p><a href="https://markdown.com.cn/">https://markdown.com.cn</a><br><a href="mailto:&#x66;&#x61;&#107;&#x65;&#x40;&#101;&#x78;&#x61;&#x6d;&#112;&#108;&#x65;&#x2e;&#x63;&#111;&#x6d;">fake@example.com</a></p>
<h1 id="代办标签"><a href="#代办标签" class="headerlink" title="代办标签"></a>代办标签</h1><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> []    # [X] 则是被完成状态。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>[!info] 快捷键<br>新版下是 ctrl + L</p>
</blockquote>
<ul>
<li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 正文 </li>
<li><input checked="" disabled="" type="checkbox"> 正文</li>
</ul>
<br>

<h1 id="图片对齐方式和尺寸"><a href="#图片对齐方式和尺寸" class="headerlink" title="图片对齐方式和尺寸"></a>图片对齐方式和尺寸</h1><ul>
<li><p>使用<a href="https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=11634006&content_type=Answer&match_order=1&q=img%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE&zd_token=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJ6aGlkYV9zZXJ2ZXIiLCJleHAiOjE3Nzc0NTQ2NTMsInEiOiJpbWfmoIfnrb4iLCJ6aGlkYV9zb3VyY2UiOiJlbnRpdHkiLCJjb250ZW50X2lkIjoxMTYzNDAwNiwiY29udGVudF90eXBlIjoiQW5zd2VyIiwibWF0Y2hfb3JkZXIiOjEsInpkX3Rva2VuIjpudWxsfQ.x1Xq70vmBr6zF-e-xFwNcEE9XpiXGQRSOuKKd7TU1Ig&zhida_source=entity">img标签</a></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;./xxx.png&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span> = <span class="string">&quot;300&quot;</span> <span class="attr">height</span> = <span class="string">&quot;200&quot;</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">&quot;图片名称&quot;</span> <span class="attr">align</span>=<span class="string">center</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>**附：**如果需要居中的话只要在外面包围div标签即可</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>  <span class="attr">align</span>=<span class="string">&quot;center&quot;</span>&gt;</span>    # left or right</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
</ul>
]]></content>
      <categories>
        <category>技术杂谈</category>
      </categories>
      <tags>
        <tag>Markdown</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>HEXO-部署的问题</title>
    <url>/posts/20260425161201-58300.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>部署到Github所遇到的一些问题。</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h1 id="网站搭建"><a href="#网站搭建" class="headerlink" title="网站搭建"></a>网站搭建</h1><p>搭建Hexo个人网站教程见：<a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/">文档 | Hexo</a></p>
<p>部署详细教程见：<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/688349142">HEXO系列教程 | 使用GitHub部署静态博客HEXO | 小白向教程 - 知乎</a></p>
<h1 id="网站部署在Github"><a href="#网站部署在Github" class="headerlink" title="网站部署在Github"></a>网站部署在Github</h1><h2 id="Github设置"><a href="#Github设置" class="headerlink" title="Github设置"></a>Github设置</h2><ol>
<li>创建一个Github账号，然后在github左侧点击<code>new</code>，创建一个新的仓库。</li>
<li>仓库名称（Repository name)，必须是<code>用户名.github.io</code>。</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
